{"tid":2296984,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"正妹拿iPhone7堅持不換i12！ 「真實原因」萬一素顏Face ID打不開，會很受傷的吧....","createTime":"2020-11-23T02:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T03:25:26.000Z","uid":178875,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"683401b57f229cc05420aabcb269529aa7eb3ea9","tid":2296984,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:44:21.000Z","msg":"蘋果今年推出全新iPhone12機款，一共分為四種機型，包含iPhone 12、iPhone 12 Pro、iPhone 12 mini以及iPhone 12 Pro Max，開賣後至今，許多果粉們也都陸續拿到了新手機，不過，近日一名網友表示自己現在拿iPhone7快撐不住了，想換i12卻沒勇氣，原因曝光後引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n我是廣告 請繼續往下閱讀<br />\n<br />\n原PO在「爆廢1公社」貼文指出<span class=\"red\">「最近看好多人都換了iPhone 12了，自己現在拿iPhone 7已經快到服役年限，但是我不敢換的原因就是因為iPhone 12是Touch ID呀！我自認妝前妝後差不了多少....但朋友都說我素顏跟鬼ㄧ樣，萬一素顏Face ID打不開，會很受傷的吧....」。</span><br />\n<br />\n▲有網友分享自己不敢換iPhone<br />\n▲有網友分享自己不敢換iPhone 12的原因在於害怕自己卸妝後解不開手機鎖。（示意圖／翻攝自《香港01》）<br />\n<br />\n貼文一出，網友紛紛回應<span class=\"red\">「笑死！怎麼會有這種考量」、「今年聽過不換手機最瞎的理由XD」、「有這檔事....如果跟鬼一樣也得面對呀！那是妳啊」、「真的快笑死，還有這種原因不換手機」、「建議可以換iPhone 8怎麼樣哈哈」、「這考量太瞎了哈哈哈」。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，也有過來人建議「可以設定兩組Face ID的！我素顏前後都給他設定了！誰敢說我解不開」、「兩組Face ID+1，就說蘋果很貼心XD」、「有兩組Face ID可以設定，就別擔心了啦哈哈」、「我也是設定兩組，畢竟在家耍廢也想要快速解鎖的哈哈」。（編輯：張嘉哲）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/5119230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F5119230&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT09C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=8288e0f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/5119230</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條女好誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a090acd94138a7d50e515e468bb7c499ac05200d","tid":2296984,"uid":157793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:48:50.000Z","msg":"正妹？你老母正啲"},{"pid":"cda10017f9adf36e5b6623d17ce261455b90f9eb","tid":2296984,"uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"台灣弱智新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96da8815c943785d7242d3f6884a48ff710013b6","tid":2296984,"uid":47186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"我入到黎"},{"pid":"9d7e469e0597197d7f5e48ede6eb0e063a8eba95","tid":2296984,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96da8815c943785d7242d3f6884a48ff710013b6","tid":2296984,"uid":47186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"我入到黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NmSLJKi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNmSLJKi.gif&h=72dd9f36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2ca867e863706e6e47ee377ea13e32e04abebc7","tid":2296984,"uid":119299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"iPhone se2: Am I a joy to you? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db24a884b487eacc05bde04047d013e1985e5e7","tid":2296984,"uid":119299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2ca867e863706e6e47ee377ea13e32e04abebc7","tid":2296984,"uid":119299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"iPhone se2: Am I a joy to you? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:25:26.000Z","msg":"Joke*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}